<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About — Pitt Stop Ministries</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/pittstop.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/nav.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/footer.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/nav') %>

    <main id="pittstop-main">
        <!-- HERO -->
        <section class="ps-hero">
            <div class="ps-hero-text">
                <p class="ps-eyebrow">The Pitt Stop</p>
                <!-- Placeholder copy — swap for Pastor Q's confirmed words -->
                <h1>Every soul needs a pit stop.</h1>
                <p class="ps-lead">A place to pull off the road, refuel on the Word, get repaired, and head back out stronger. That's what Pitt Stop Ministries is built to be.</p>
                <div class="ps-cta">
                    <a class="ps-btn ps-btn-primary" href="/sermons">Watch a message</a>
                    <a class="ps-btn ps-btn-ghost" href="/contacts">Plan a visit</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <figure class="ps-hero-photo">
                <img src="/images/pop-picture.jpg" alt="Pastor Q of Pitt Stop Ministries" loading="lazy">
                <figcaption>Pastor Q</figcaption>
            </figure>
        </section>

        <!-- STORY -->
        <section class="ps-story">
            <h2 class="ps-section-title">Our Heart</h2>
            <!-- Placeholder copy — Don / Pastor Q to confirm -->
            <p>Pitt Stop Ministries exists to bring God's people back to the Kingdom!<br>to meet you right where you are on the road and point you home.</p>
            <p>Led by Pastor Q, we believe no one was meant to run on empty. <br>Whatever mile you're on, there's a place for you here.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- VALUES -->
        <section class="ps-values">
            <article class="ps-value">
                <h3>Refuel</h3>
                <p>Be filled by the Word and worship, every week.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="ps-value">
                <h3>Repair</h3>
                <p>Find healing, prayer, and a family that walks with you.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="ps-value">
                <h3>Send out</h3>
                <p>Get equipped and head back out to do what <strong>HE</strong> wants to do through you.</p>
            </article>
        </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <script src="/js/nav.js" defer></script>
</body>
</html>
